
School zones : 
- SLOW DOWN and WATCH FOR CHILDREN 
- 15 or 25 mph (not in effect after hours (530p) unless otherwise posted)
- FLASHING yellow road lights : speed limit is in effect
- NO U-TURNS 
- Until the crossing guard (person) is on a side , stop and wait 

School buses :
- stop when
  - around a loading or unloading bus
  - flashing red signal
  - take off once the signal is out
  - do not stop on a divided highway 

